{"tid":518572,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"終結三星獨霸，傳 LG 將分食 2018 年 6.5 吋 iPhone X Plus OLED 訂單","createTime":"2018-01-03T13:16:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T04:51:58.000Z","uid":47132,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b58f1d232308dac48348b30eb7562a859c70b1b8","tid":518572,"uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T13:16:16.000Z","msg":"LG Display（LGD）傳今年將正式成為新 iPhone OLED 面板第二供應商，儘管初期供應量不大，但仍將終結三星獨霸蘋果 OLED 面板訂單的局面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/o468K7R.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fo468K7R.gif&h=bce84eec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南韓科技媒體 ETnews 報導，按照目前 iPhone X 的出貨規模，蘋果對 LG Display 的下單量將介於 1,500-1,600 萬片之間，據傳 LG Display 正積極向蘋果爭取增加訂單，顯示對自家產品相當有信心，讓三星倍感威脅，預料兩公司未來競爭只會有增無減。<br />\n<br />\nLG Display 產能較少，傳將與三星 Display 分攤 6.5 吋版 iPhone OLED 螢幕訂單，主要供應商三星 Display 則同時負責滿足 5.8 吋或 6 吋 iPhone 的 OLED 面板需求。<br />\n<br />\nLG Display 旗下 E6 廠將在第二季量產首批 OLED 面板，該廠每月 OLED 軟板產能達 3 萬單位，若以良率與產出均為 100% 估計，每月可生產 594 萬片 6 吋 OLED 面板。"},{"pid":"201e609bf51751644f5ed2d8e3bbf4b02c8f8526","tid":518572,"uid":3032,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T13:17:34.000Z","msg":"LG oled仲衰撚過三叔<br />\n不了"},{"pid":"545032896ee49ae48f69e70b648c9a8f6956e809","tid":518572,"uid":137694,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T13:17:39.000Z","msg":"寧願三星獨大好過用lg啲垃圾芒<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f558f800a85cade3cabc9ed925b2fb51f2994154","tid":518572,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T13:17:49.000Z","msg":"LG d垃圾咪搞"},{"pid":"204da50b6f5af4c1e01a7ca5e60aad917179afbe","tid":518572,"uid":2373,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T13:41:44.000Z","msg":"又有得抽獎了<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93475ebc64b78bd2ca52113e2d83235640d9eeb0","tid":518572,"uid":52068,"like":4,"dislike":3,"sco